text: Colobothea sinaloensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Giesbert in 1979. It is known from Mexico.BioLib.cz - Colobothea sinaloensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1979
